      • getExternalProjectConfigToUse

        protected abstract java.io.File getExternalProjectConfigToUse(java.io.File file)
        Allows to adjust external project config file to use on the basis of the given value.

        Example: a user might choose a directory which contains target config file and particular implementation expands that to a particular file under the directory.

        Parameters:
        file - base external project config file
        Returns:
        external project config file to use
